# Coffee Roasting Data Management System

This repository demonstrates how to manage, analyze, and visualize coffee roasting data. It is part of a project to optimize coffee roasting processes for consistent quality.

## Features
1. Structured database schema for storing coffee temperature and roasting parameters.
2. Real-time data ingestion using Python and MySQL.
3. Analytical tools for evaluating roasting patterns and trends.
4. Docker environment for easy database setup.
